## Proposed Changes

We will construct a monorepo setup using **npm workspaces** containing the Next.js application, FastAPI app, compiler runner, shared configurations, and docker assets.

```
pypocket/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/           # Next.js Frontend (React, Tailwind, Framer Motion, PWA)
│   ├── api/           # FastAPI Backend (Python, SQLAlchemy, PostgreSQL, Redis)
│   ├── compiler/      # Sandbox Code Execution Microservice (Python, Docker Runner)
│   └── admin/         # Admin Analytics & Dashboard (Integrated as a route or sub-app)
├── packages/
│   ├── ui/            # Reusable UI component templates
│   ├── config/        # Base ESLint, Tailwind, TypeScript configs
│   └── types/         # Share DB/API TypeScript schemas
├── docker/            # Docker configurations (PostgreSQL, Redis, Sandbox environments)
├── docs/              # System documentation
└── README.md
```

### Database Schema

We will initialize a PostgreSQL database with SQLAlchemy models in `apps/api/app/database/models.py`.

```mermaid
erDiagram
    users ||--o| profiles : has
    users ||--o{ lesson_progress : tracks
    users ||--o{ quiz_attempts : submits
    users ||--o{ project_submissions : uploads
    users ||--o{ user_badges : earns
    users ||--o{ saved_codes : stores
    users ||--o{ compiler_sessions : runs
    users ||--o| daily_streaks : maintains
    users ||--o{ xp_history : records
    users ||--o{ coins : accumulates
    users ||--o{ certificates : holds
    users ||--o{ notifications : receives
    courses ||--o{ chapters : contains
    chapters ||--o{ lessons : contains
    lessons ||--o{ quiz_attempts : contains
    lessons ||--o{ saved_codes : contains
```

* **users**: User authentication details (ID, Email, Hashed Password, Roles, JWT metadata)
* **profiles**: User details (Avatar, Bio, Skills, GitHub, LinkedIn, Portfolio, Level, XP, Coins)
* **courses & chapters & lessons**: Structure of Python Basics, OOP, Flask, SQL, Django, Career roadmap, etc.
* **lesson_progress**: Completed status, notes, rating.
* **saved_codes & compiler_sessions**: User's compiled python code for each lesson.
* **daily_streaks**: Calculates streak counts, last active timestamps.
* **xp_history & coins**: Detailed audit of XP and Coins gained.
* **badges & user_badges**: Gamified achievements.
* **certificates**: PDF generator reference with UUID, QR-code hash.
* **discussions & comments**: Community boards.

