### Automated Tests
- Backend pytest test suite testing JWT Auth, database insertions, and Redis streak calculations.
- Compiler tests running recursive tests, slow infinite loops (`while True:` to confirm timeout), file system blockages, and network blockages.
- Next.js build validation and typescript validation checks.

### Manual Verification
- View viewport responsiveness across simulated mobile sizes: 320px (SE), 390px (iPhone 13), 412px (Samsung), and 768px (iPad).
- Test Pyodide compiler offline by toggling Network Offline in Chrome Developer Tools.
- Validate gamification confetti trigger when completing a sample lesson module.
